{
  "title": "Olympian Baby",
  "description": "Lee Chan had gradually been falling for Taesan, the hyung who had once saved him when everyone else ignored and let him down, and who he had admired for as long as he could remember.\nBut did Taesan ever notice how Chan felt?\n[I need a small break. Please don’t look for me.]\nThen one day, Taesan, who was winning victory after victory as an athlete of the national olympic taekwondo team, vanished without a trace.\nYears passed and Chan searched everywhere for the person who had suddenly disappeared from his life. Until, by sheer chance, he comes across Taesan again in a quiet town hosting the National Sports Festival.\n'Um… who are you?'\nBut Taesan doesn’t recognize Chan at all. And he's holding a baby who looks just like himself…?!",
